PLEASE NOTE
 
This is a medical chat bot trained by doctors.
 
You can simply ask a question (“How can I book an appointment”?), request some information (“Tell me about asthma”) or briefly describe the main symptom worrying you (“I have a headache”).
 
Please only tell me the symptom that’s bothering you the most.
 
we need to let you know that this service is still learning about symptoms in pregnancy, skin problems and mental health issues.
 
If you have any questions, please see Help.
 
If this is an emergency, please call 999.
